TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: select LTRIM(RTRIM(dc_id)), LTRIM(RTRIM(dc_name)) from ( select distinct LTRIM(RTRIM(oodc)) as dc_id, LTRIM(RTRIM(oofacd)) as dc_name from bidssdta.bit054pf union select distinct LTRIM(RTRIM(ssdc)) as dc_id, LTRIM(RTRIM(ssfacd)) as dc_name from bidssdta.bit051pf where ssorig = 0 )v

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT SLBA_FACILITY.FACILITY_ID as FACILITY_ID, SLBA_FACILITY.FACILITY_CODE as FACILITY_CODE, SLBA_FACILITY.FACILITY_NAME as FACILITY_NAME FROM SLBA_FACILITY SLBA_FACILITY --WHERE --SLBA_FACILITY.UPDATE_USERID='MX_GM_ETL'
